<p>&#8216;New guidance on the advice given by government lawyers aims to instil a more “private sector” approach to client service seen in law firms, the Attorney General said yesterday. Suella Braverman said she wanted to move away from the &#8220;computer says no&#8221; response that has “hampered” ministers.&#8217;</p>
